text.section:
The Cabinet for Health and Family Services shall promulgate administrative regulations relating to:
Health and cleanliness of places of business in which tattooing, body piercing, or both are conducted;
Sterilization of tattooing and body piercing apparatus;
Procedures to prevent the spread of disease or infection during or relating to tattooing and body piercing procedures;
Procedures to prevent any tattooing or body piercing of minors without the written notarized consent of a custodial parent or legal guardian; and
Such other administrative regulations as may be necessary to protect public health or properly administer the program requirements of this section.
